README.md
     1вҶ’# humanize
    12вҶ’This modest package contains various common humanization utilities, like turning a
    13вҶ’number into a fuzzy human-readable duration ("3 minutes ago") or into a human-readable
    14вҶ’size or throughput. It is localized to:
    15вҶ’
    16вҶ’- Arabic
    17вҶ’- Basque
    18вҶ’- Bengali
    19вҶ’- Brazilian Portuguese
    20вҶ’- Catalan
    21вҶ’- Danish
    22вҶ’- Dutch
    23вҶ’- Esperanto
    24вҶ’- European Portuguese
    25вҶ’- Finnish
    26вҶ’- French
    27вҶ’- German
    28вҶ’- Greek
    29вҶ’- Hebrew
    30вҶ’- Indonesian
    31вҶ’- Italian
    32вҶ’- Japanese
    33вҶ’- Klingon
    34вҶ’- Korean
    35вҶ’- Norwegian
    36вҶ’- Persian
    37вҶ’- Polish
    38вҶ’- Russian
    39вҶ’- Simplified Chinese
    40вҶ’- Slovak
    41вҶ’- Slovenian
    42вҶ’- Spanish
    43вҶ’- Swedish
    44вҶ’- Turkish
    45вҶ’- Ukrainian
    46вҶ’- Uzbek
    47вҶ’- Vietnamese
    48вҶ’
    49вҶ’## API reference
    51вҶ’[https://humanize.readthedocs.io](https://humanize.readthedocs.io/)
    52вҶ’
    53вҶ’<!-- usage-start -->
    54вҶ’
    55вҶ’## Installation
    57вҶ’### From PyPI
    59вҶ’```bash
    60вҶ’python3 -m pip install --upgrade humanize
    61вҶ’```
    62вҶ’
    63вҶ’### From source
    65вҶ’```bash
    66вҶ’git clone https://github.com/python-humanize/humanize
    67вҶ’cd humanize
    68вҶ’python3 -m pip install -e .
    69вҶ’```
    70вҶ’
    71вҶ’## Usage
    73вҶ’### Integer humanization
    75вҶ’```pycon
    76вҶ’>>> import humanize
    77вҶ’>>> humanize.intcomma(12345)
    78вҶ’'12,345'
    79вҶ’>>> humanize.intword(123455913)
    80вҶ’'123.5 million'
    81вҶ’>>> humanize.intword(12345591313)
    82вҶ’'12.3 billion'
    83вҶ’>>> humanize.apnumber(4)
    84вҶ’'four'
    85вҶ’>>> humanize.apnumber(41)
    86вҶ’'41'
    87вҶ’```
    88вҶ’
    89вҶ’### Date & time humanization
    91вҶ’```pycon
    92вҶ’>>> import humanize
    93вҶ’>>> import datetime as dt
    94вҶ’>>> humanize.naturalday(dt.datetime.now())
    95вҶ’'today'
    96вҶ’>>> humanize.naturaldelta(dt.timedelta(seconds=1001))
    97вҶ’'16 minutes'
    98вҶ’>>> humanize.naturalday(dt.datetime.now() - dt.timedelta(days=1))
    99вҶ’'yesterday'
   100вҶ’>>> humanize.naturalday(dt.date(2007, 6, 5))
   101вҶ’'Jun 05'
   102вҶ’>>> humanize.naturaldate(dt.date(2007, 6, 5))
   103вҶ’'Jun 05 2007'
   104вҶ’>>> humanize.naturaltime(dt.datetime.now() - dt.timedelta(seconds=1))
   105вҶ’'a second ago'
   106вҶ’>>> humanize.naturaltime(dt.datetime.now() - dt.timedelta(seconds=3600))
   107вҶ’'an hour ago'
   108вҶ’```
   109вҶ’
   110вҶ’### Precise time delta
   112вҶ’```pycon
   113вҶ’>>> import humanize
   114вҶ’>>> import datetime as dt
   115вҶ’>>> delta = dt.timedelta(seconds=3633, days=2, microseconds=123000)
   116вҶ’>>> humanize.precisedelta(delta)
   117вҶ’'2 days, 1 hour and 33.12 seconds'
   118вҶ’>>> humanize.precisedelta(delta, minimum_unit="microseconds")
   119вҶ’'2 days, 1 hour, 33 seconds and 123 milliseconds'
   120вҶ’>>> humanize.precisedelta(delta, suppress=["days"], format="%0.4f")
   121вҶ’'49 hours and 33.1230 seconds'
   122вҶ’```
   123вҶ’
   124вҶ’#### Smaller units
   126вҶ’If seconds are too large, set `minimum_unit` to milliseconds or microseconds:
   127вҶ’
   128вҶ’```pycon
   129вҶ’>>> import humanize
   130вҶ’>>> import datetime as dt
   131вҶ’>>> humanize.naturaldelta(dt.timedelta(seconds=2))
   132вҶ’'2 seconds'
   133вҶ’```
   134вҶ’
   135вҶ’```pycon
   136вҶ’>>> delta = dt.timedelta(milliseconds=4)
   137вҶ’>>> humanize.naturaldelta(delta)
   138вҶ’'a moment'
   139вҶ’>>> humanize.naturaldelta(delta, minimum_unit="milliseconds")
   140вҶ’'4 milliseconds'
   141вҶ’>>> humanize.naturaldelta(delta, minimum_unit="microseconds")
   142вҶ’'4 milliseconds'
   143вҶ’```
   144вҶ’
   145вҶ’```pycon
   146вҶ’>>> humanize.naturaltime(delta)
   147вҶ’'now'
   148вҶ’>>> humanize.naturaltime(delta, minimum_unit="milliseconds")
   149вҶ’'4 milliseconds ago'
   150вҶ’>>> humanize.naturaltime(delta, minimum_unit="microseconds")
   151вҶ’'4 milliseconds ago'
   152вҶ’```
   153вҶ’
   154вҶ’### File size humanization
   156вҶ’```pycon
   157вҶ’>>> import humanize
   158вҶ’>>> humanize.naturalsize(1_000_000)
   159вҶ’'1.0 MB'
   160вҶ’>>> humanize.naturalsize(1_000_000, binary=True)
   161вҶ’'976.6 KiB'
   162вҶ’>>> humanize.naturalsize(1_000_000, gnu=True)
   163вҶ’'976.6K'
   164вҶ’```
   165вҶ’
   166вҶ’### Human-readable floating point numbers
   168вҶ’```pycon
   169вҶ’>>> import humanize
   170вҶ’>>> humanize.fractional(1/3)
   171вҶ’'1/3'
   172вҶ’>>> humanize.fractional(1.5)
   173вҶ’'1 1/2'
   174вҶ’>>> humanize.fractional(0.3)
   175вҶ’'3/10'
   176вҶ’>>> humanize.fractional(0.333)
   177вҶ’'333/1000'
   178вҶ’>>> humanize.fractional(1)
   179вҶ’'1'
   180вҶ’```
   181вҶ’
   182вҶ’### Scientific notation
   184вҶ’```pycon
   185вҶ’>>> import humanize
   186вҶ’>>> humanize.scientific(0.3)
   187вҶ’'3.00 x 10вҒ»В№'
   188вҶ’>>> humanize.scientific(500)
   189вҶ’'5.00 x 10ВІ'
   190вҶ’>>> humanize.scientific("20000")
   191вҶ’'2.00 x 10вҒҙ'
   192вҶ’>>> humanize.scientific(1**10)
   193вҶ’'1.00 x 10вҒ°'
   194вҶ’>>> humanize.scientific(1**10, precision=1)
   195вҶ’'1.0 x 10вҒ°'
   196вҶ’>>> humanize.scientific(1**10, precision=0)
   197вҶ’'1 x 10вҒ°'
   198вҶ’```
   199вҶ’
   200вҶ’## Localization
   202вҶ’How to change locale at runtime:
   203вҶ’
   204вҶ’```pycon
   205вҶ’>>> import humanize
   206вҶ’>>> import datetime as dt
   207вҶ’>>> humanize.naturaltime(dt.timedelta(seconds=3))
   208вҶ’'3 seconds ago'
   209вҶ’>>> _t = humanize.i18n.activate("ru_RU")
   210вҶ’>>> humanize.naturaltime(dt.timedelta(seconds=3))
   211вҶ’'3 СҒРөРәСғРҪРҙСӢ РҪР°Р·Р°Рҙ'
   212вҶ’>>> humanize.i18n.deactivate()
   213вҶ’>>> humanize.naturaltime(dt.timedelta(seconds=3))
   214вҶ’'3 seconds ago'
   215вҶ’```
   216вҶ’
   217вҶ’You can pass additional parameter `path` to `activate` to specify a path to search
   218вҶ’locales in.
   219вҶ’
   220вҶ’```pycon
   221вҶ’>>> import humanize
   222вҶ’>>> humanize.i18n.activate("xx_XX")
   223вҶ’<...>
   224вҶ’FileNotFoundError: [Errno 2] No translation file found for domain: 'humanize'
   225вҶ’>>> humanize.i18n.activate("pt_BR", path="path/to/my/own/translation/")
   226вҶ’<gettext.GNUTranslations instance ...>
   227вҶ’```
   228вҶ’
   229вҶ’<!-- usage-end -->
   230вҶ’
